MID_支援_エリーゼ_レオン_Ｂ: $t1$Wmエリーゼ|7$Wmレオン|3$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E笑,|$w0|Leon!\nThere's something I want you to tell me.$k\n$Wsレオン|$WaElise.\nWhat is it today?$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Right, tell me about our father\nback when he was younger! $k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E怒,|Our father when he was younger?$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E通常,|That's right!\nI only heard a little about him from Marx.$k$pWhen father was young\nhe was quite different, right?$k$p$E笑,|How was he before?$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E通常,|Hmm...\nUntil the queen died...$k$p...Father was a gentle person.$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E怒2,汗|Gentle!?\nNo way... That's hard to imagine.$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E笑,|I know it's hard to believe,\nbut I was quite fond of him back then.$k$pWhen I was little, I rode on his\nshoulders and he would pat my head.$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$Eびっくり,汗|Whaat? That sounds great!\nI've never gotten that...!$k$pWhat else? What else?$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$Eキメ,|I hear he was a brave person,\nwhen he was fighting on the front lines.$k$pI don't remember much\nabout this side of him, but...$k$pWhen he would come with me to contests,\nI always thought he was a strong person.$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E通常,|Yeah... but I can't see him like that,\nwhen he almost never leaves his room.$k$p$E笑,|I wish I could see what\nfather was like back then!$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E笑,|Yeah...\nI also wonder if it was true.$k$p$E通常,|Hmm... anything else... oh!$k$p$Eキメ,|When father was young,\nhe also had a lot of love affairs.$k$pHe would woo many women, but often\ncut off ties with them afterwards.$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$Eキメ,|What...!?\nOur father was popular?!$k\n$Wsレオン|$WaIt's only natural, since he's the king.\nHe was an attractive person.$k$p$E通常,|Because of that, there was fierce\ncompetition for his affections.$k$pThe bad relationships between\nthe concubines lead to killing.$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E怒2,汗|That is...!\nThey killed each other?!$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E怒,|It just couldn't be helped.$k$pIn order to raise their status,\nthey had to make use of a king's child.$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E落胆,|Oh...$k$p…………$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E通常,|Elise?$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E通常,|Nope, it's nothing!$k$p$E笑,|Oh, it's almost time for the meal!\nIf I don't hurry they'll run out of food.$k$pThank you for telling\nme about father, Leon!$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$Eキメ,|Oh... Huh.$k
MID_支援_エリーゼ_レオン_Ａ: $t1$Wmエリーゼ|7$E落胆,|$Wmレオン|3$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$w0|...Leon.$k\n$Wsレオン|$WaElise. Did you come to ask\nabout something again today?$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$WaYes...$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E怒,|...?\nWhat is it?$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E怒2,|U-um, do you think us siblings are\ngoing to get along well forever?$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E通常,汗|What's with that all of a sudden?$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E落胆,|I thought about it before, when\nI'd heard that story from you.$k$pIf we would always remain like this...$k$pBecause, me and Leon were\nborn to different mothers...$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E怒,|Well, that's...true.$k$pBoth you and I, and even Camilla are\nthe children of separate concubines.$k$pAnd, they weren't that close...right?$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa…………$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E通常,|We can talk like this now but,\nbefore you were born...$k$pThe fight between the concubines\ngot so terribly horrid that...$k$peven the siblings couldn't even\ntalk tenderly to one another...$k$p$E怒,|Especially because I was a boy, I had a\nlot of the makings to stand superior.$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E怒2,汗|Leon...$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E苦,|That's why, I never loved my mother.$k$pSaying this is weird, but...$k$pI thought that she was using me as a tool\nto get to Father...until the very end.$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa…………$k$p$E落胆,|...I can understand that feeling.$k$pI loved my mother, but the one\nMother loved was always Father.$k$pMy mother got a bad illness and before\nshe died, it wasn't my name she said...$k$pbut Father's name...$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E怒,|Really...$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E苦,|Because of that, I was nervous.$k$pLike when I thought I would have to\nmutually kill the siblings I didn't know...$k$p...That we couldn't stay like this.$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E通常,|What are you saying.\nWe have no relation to them.$k$pWhoever fought over us in our birthplace,\nit's meaningless to us.$k$p$E怒,|And above that, for our blood relation and\nmothers and origins to influence us now...$k$pI don't think that'll happen.$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E怒2,汗|Really? Do you really think that?$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$Eキメ,|Yes.$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E通常,|I'm glad... Really, I think the same!$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E怒,汗|Haah? Then why did you\nspecifically come to ask me?$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E笑,|Because, I thought that what\nI was thinking might be wrong.$k$p$Eキメ,|But...what Leon says is never wrong.$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$Eキメ,|You put a lot of trust in me.$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E笑,|Of course! That's because I love Leon.$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E通常,|For you to believe in someone for those\nreasons, you really are still a child, Elise.$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E怒,|If I couldn't believe in Leon,\nthen I'd happily stay a child forever.$k$pIf all of us don't get along, I'd rather die.$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E苦,汗|You're exaggerating again.$k$p$E通常,|...But, even if just one sibling\nthinks like that, I think we'll be fine.$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$Eびっくり,|Really?!$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$Eキメ,|Yeah. Even if we're only half-related\nby our blood, and not fully...$k$pIf we all accept each other,\nthose bonds can't be broken.$k$p$E笑,|Us siblings are going\nto be like this forever.$k$pSo from now on, no matter what path\nwe pick, nothing will change, right?$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$E笑,|Woah...\nThat's kind of amazing.$k$pIf Leon says that, then I feel\nlike that's definitely right!$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E怒,照|But, don't talk about what we said\ntoday to Marx and the others, okay?$k$pI said some things that are out of\ncharacter for me. It's quite embarrassing.$k\n$Wsエリーゼ|$Wa$Eキメ,|I got it. It's a secret just between us!\nThank you, Leon!$k$p$E笑,|From now on, with everyone...\nLet's get along well!$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E笑,|Yes, of course.$k
